purpose DO a practical to install SMPS. 
=> NorthBridge connects the CPU directly to high-bandwidth components like RAM andgraphics. It acts as the "memory controller hub" for fast data transfer. SMPS is Switched-Mode-Power-Supply.It converts high-voltage AC from the wall to low-voltage DC (e.g., 3.3V, 5V, 12V) needed by components.
 Practical: Connect 24-pin motherboard power, 8-pin CPU power, SATA/Molex for drives, PCIe for GPU. Secure with screws. 

