39) What are the parts of a laptop? 
=>Screen, keyboard/touchpad, battery, motherboard, RAM, storage (SSD), CPU/GPU, cooling fan, hinges, ports, webcam, speakers.

40) Do a practical to disassemble the laptop.
=>Remove battery, bottom screws/panel. Disconnect internals carefully (trackpad, keyboard, display cable). Remove components like RAM, SSD, fan.


